{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012YHiFH6euc6GyPS8PmjyWc","type":"tool_result","content":"     1ŌåÆ# Session Issues Log ŌĆö 2026-03-24\n     2ŌåÆ\n     3ŌåÆ### 11-3-state-reconciliation-on-session-start ŌĆö create-story (2026-03-24T11:34:00Z)\n     4ŌåÆ\n     5ŌåÆ- Epic definition had only 1 AC; expanded to 12 ACs by examining codebase\n     6ŌåÆ- Risk: parseStoryKey() returns [Infinity, Infinity] for non-matching keys ŌĆö edge case needs handling\n     7ŌåÆ- Risk: orphan file deletion (ACs 3-4) is one-way; must delete AFTER successful state write\n     8ŌåÆ- writeStateAtomic() already calls writeSprintStatusYaml() ŌĆö reconcileState() may cause double YAML generation\n     9ŌåÆ- retry-state.ts has @deprecated comments saying \"will be removed in story 11-3\" for legacy path helpers\n    10ŌåÆ- run.ts still reads ralph/.flagged_stories directly (line 93-101), bypassing sprint-state.json flagged field ŌĆö must update before file deletion\n    11ŌåÆ\n    12ŌåÆ### 11-3-state-reconciliation-on-session-start ŌĆö dev-story (2026-03-24T11:45:00Z)\n    13ŌåÆ\n    14ŌåÆ- Pre-existing ~60 type errors in unrelated test files (not introduced by this story)\n    15ŌåÆ- Readonly mutation workaround: uses JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(...)) deep clone + type assertions to mutate SprintState clone\n    16ŌåÆ- YAML always regenerated even in no-op case ŌĆö cheap but could be optimized to skip if content unchanged\n    17ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"010b7052-acb2-4a98-9861-0b5f61bbdbf0","uuid":"64262b24-7d34-4325-8e5c-c405dd982bbe","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:58:03.682Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log ŌĆö 2026-03-24\n\n### 11-3-state-reconciliation-on-session-start ŌĆö create-story (2026-03-24T11:34:00Z)\n\n- Epic definition had only 1 AC; expanded to 12 ACs by examining codebase\n- Risk: parseStoryKey() returns [Infinity, Infinity] for non-matching keys ŌĆö edge case needs handling\n- Risk: orphan file deletion (ACs 3-4) is one-way; must delete AFTER successful state write\n- writeStateAtomic() already calls writeSprintStatusYaml() ŌĆö reconcileState() may cause double YAML generation\n- retry-state.ts has @deprecated comments saying \"will be removed in story 11-3\" for legacy path helpers\n- run.ts still reads ralph/.flagged_stories directly (line 93-101), bypassing sprint-state.json flagged field ŌĆö must update before file deletion\n\n### 11-3-state-reconciliation-on-session-start ŌĆö dev-story (2026-03-24T11:45:00Z)\n\n- Pre-existing ~60 type errors in unrelated test files (not introduced by this story)\n- Readonly mutation workaround: uses JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(...)) deep clone + type assertions to mutate SprintState clone\n- YAML always regenerated even in no-op case ŌĆö cheap but could be optimized to skip if content unchanged\n","numLines":17,"startLine":1,"totalLines":17}}}
