{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015fmgpR3sJPCoWFgvjFviN7","type":"tool_result","content":"     1ŌåÆ# Story {{epic_num}}.{{story_num}}: {{story_title}}\n     2ŌåÆ\n     3ŌåÆStatus: ready-for-dev\n     4ŌåÆ\n     5ŌåÆ<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n     6ŌåÆ\n     7ŌåÆ## Story\n     8ŌåÆ\n     9ŌåÆAs a {{role}},\n    10ŌåÆI want {{action}},\n    11ŌåÆso that {{benefit}}.\n    12ŌåÆ\n    13ŌåÆ## Acceptance Criteria\n    14ŌåÆ\n    15ŌåÆ1. [Add acceptance criteria from epics/PRD]\n    16ŌåÆ\n    17ŌåÆ## Tasks / Subtasks\n    18ŌåÆ\n    19ŌåÆ- [ ] Task 1 (AC: #)\n    20ŌåÆ  - [ ] Subtask 1.1\n    21ŌåÆ- [ ] Task 2 (AC: #)\n    22ŌåÆ  - [ ] Subtask 2.1\n    23ŌåÆ\n    24ŌåÆ## Dev Notes\n    25ŌåÆ\n    26ŌåÆ- Relevant architecture patterns and constraints\n    27ŌåÆ- Source tree components to touch\n    28ŌåÆ- Testing standards summary\n    29ŌåÆ\n    30ŌåÆ### Project Structure Notes\n    31ŌåÆ\n    32ŌåÆ- Alignment with unified project structure (paths, modules, naming)\n    33ŌåÆ- Detected conflicts or variances (with rationale)\n    34ŌåÆ\n    35ŌåÆ### References\n    36ŌåÆ\n    37ŌåÆ- Cite all technical details with source paths and sections, e.g. [Source: docs/<file>.md#Section]\n    38ŌåÆ\n    39ŌåÆ<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-START:story-verification -->\n    40ŌåÆ## Verification Requirements\n    41ŌåÆ\n    42ŌåÆ- [ ] Showboat proof document created (`docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.proof.md`)\n    43ŌåÆ- [ ] All acceptance criteria verified with real-world evidence\n    44ŌåÆ- [ ] Test coverage meets target (100%)\n    45ŌåÆ\n    46ŌåÆ## Documentation Requirements\n    47ŌåÆ\n    48ŌåÆ- [ ] Relevant AGENTS.md files updated (list modules touched)\n    49ŌåÆ- [ ] Exec-plan created in `docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.md`\n    50ŌåÆ\n    51ŌåÆ## Testing Requirements\n    52ŌåÆ\n    53ŌåÆ- [ ] Unit tests written for all new/changed code\n    54ŌåÆ- [ ] Integration tests for cross-module interactions\n    55ŌåÆ- [ ] Coverage target: 100%\n    56ŌåÆ<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n    57ŌåÆ\n    58ŌåÆ## Dev Agent Record\n    59ŌåÆ\n    60ŌåÆ### Agent Model Used\n    61ŌåÆ\n    62ŌåÆ{{agent_model_name_version}}\n    63ŌåÆ\n    64ŌåÆ### Debug Log References\n    65ŌåÆ\n    66ŌåÆ### Completion Notes List\n    67ŌåÆ\n    68ŌåÆ### File List\n    69ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01SqkcCz91dsjFJacd7fAMKf","session_id":"010b7052-acb2-4a98-9861-0b5f61bbdbf0","uuid":"b8c81788-f324-4963-b5b6-787725a2caf5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:58:49.854Z"}
