{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01N5LVdBmaDC1u9aAcGRvzY6","type":"tool_result","content":"     1ŌåÆ---\n     2ŌåÆtitle: 'Enhanced Dev Story Definition of Done Checklist'\n     3ŌåÆvalidation-target: 'Story markdown ({{story_path}})'\n     4ŌåÆvalidation-criticality: 'HIGHEST'\n     5ŌåÆrequired-inputs:\n     6ŌåÆ  - 'Story markdown file with enhanced Dev Notes containing comprehensive implementation context'\n     7ŌåÆ  - 'Completed Tasks/Subtasks section with all items marked [x]'\n     8ŌåÆ  - 'Updated File List section with all changed files'\n     9ŌåÆ  - 'Updated Dev Agent Record with implementation notes'\n    10ŌåÆoptional-inputs:\n    11ŌåÆ  - 'Test results output'\n    12ŌåÆ  - 'CI logs'\n    13ŌåÆ  - 'Linting reports'\n    14ŌåÆvalidation-rules:\n    15ŌåÆ  - 'Only permitted story sections modified: Tasks/Subtasks checkboxes, Dev Agent Record, File List, Change Log, Status'\n    16ŌåÆ  - 'All implementation requirements from story Dev Notes must be satisfied'\n    17ŌåÆ  - 'Definition of Done checklist must pass completely'\n    18ŌåÆ  - 'Enhanced story context must contain sufficient technical guidance'\n    19ŌåÆ---\n    20ŌåÆ\n    21ŌåÆ# ­¤Ä» Enhanced Definition of Done Checklist\n    22ŌåÆ\n    23ŌåÆ**Critical validation:** Story is truly ready for review only when ALL items below are satisfied\n    24ŌåÆ\n    25ŌåÆ## ­¤ōŗ Context & Requirements Validation\n    26ŌåÆ\n    27ŌåÆ- [ ] **Story Context Completeness:** Dev Notes contains ALL necessary technical requirements, architecture patterns, and implementation guidance\n    28ŌåÆ- [ ] **Architecture Compliance:** Implementation follows all architectural requirements specified in Dev Notes\n    29ŌåÆ- [ ] **Technical Specifications:** All technical specifications (libraries, frameworks, versions) from Dev Notes are implemented correctly\n    30ŌåÆ- [ ] **Previous Story Learnings:** Previous story insights incorporated (if applicable) and build upon appropriately\n    31ŌåÆ\n    32ŌåÆ## Ō£ģ Implementation Completion\n    33ŌåÆ\n    34ŌåÆ- [ ] **All Tasks Complete:** Every task and subtask marked complete with [x]\n    35ŌåÆ- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria Satisfaction:** Implementation satisfies EVERY Acceptance Criterion in the story\n    36ŌåÆ- [ ] **No Ambiguous Implementation:** Clear, unambiguous implementation that meets story requirements\n    37ŌåÆ- [ ] **Edge Cases Handled:** Error conditions and edge cases appropriately addressed\n    38ŌåÆ- [ ] **Dependencies Within Scope:** Only uses dependencies specified in story or project-context.md\n    39ŌåÆ\n    40ŌåÆ## ­¤¦¬ Testing & Quality Assurance\n    41ŌåÆ\n    42ŌåÆ- [ ] **Unit Tests:** Unit tests added/updated for ALL core functionality introduced/changed by this story\n    43ŌåÆ- [ ] **Integration Tests:** Integration tests added/updated for component interactions when story requirements demand them\n    44ŌåÆ- [ ] **End-to-End Tests:** End-to-end tests created for critical user flows when story requirements specify them\n    45ŌåÆ- [ ] **Test Coverage:** Tests cover acceptance criteria and edge cases from story Dev Notes\n    46ŌåÆ- [ ] **Regression Prevention:** ALL existing tests pass (no regressions introduced)\n    47ŌåÆ- [ ] **Code Quality:** Linting and static checks pass when configured in project\n    48ŌåÆ- [ ] **Test Framework Compliance:** Tests use project's testing frameworks and patterns from Dev Notes\n    49ŌåÆ\n    50ŌåÆ## ­¤ōØ Documentation & Tracking\n    51ŌåÆ\n    52ŌåÆ- [ ] **File List Complete:** File List includes EVERY new, modified, or deleted file (paths relative to repo root)\n    53ŌåÆ- [ ] **Dev Agent Record Updated:** Contains relevant Implementation Notes and/or Debug Log for this work\n    54ŌåÆ- [ ] **Change Log Updated:** Change Log includes clear summary of what changed and why\n    55ŌåÆ- [ ] **Review Follow-ups:** All review follow-up tasks (marked [AI-Review]) completed and corresponding review items marked resolved (if applicable)\n    56ŌåÆ- [ ] **Story Structure Compliance:** Only permitted sections of story file were modified\n    57ŌåÆ\n    58ŌåÆ## ­¤öÜ Final Status Verification\n    59ŌåÆ\n    60ŌåÆ- [ ] **Story Status Updated:** Story Status set to \"review\"\n    61ŌåÆ- [ ] **Sprint Status Updated:** Sprint status updated to \"review\" (when sprint tracking is used)\n    62ŌåÆ- [ ] **Quality Gates Passed:** All quality checks and validations completed successfully\n    63ŌåÆ- [ ] **No HALT Conditions:** No blocking issues or incomplete work remaining\n    64ŌåÆ- [ ] **User Communication Ready:** Implementation summary prepared for user review\n    65ŌåÆ\n    66ŌåÆ## ­¤Ä» Final Validation Output\n    67ŌåÆ\n    68ŌåÆ```\n    69ŌåÆDefinition of Done: {{PASS/FAIL}}\n    70ŌåÆ\n    71ŌåÆŌ£ģ **Story Ready for Review:** {{story_key}}\n    72ŌåÆ­¤ōŖ **Completion Score:** {{completed_items}}/{{total_items}} items passed\n    73ŌåÆ­¤öŹ **Quality Gates:** {{quality_gates_status}}\n    74ŌåÆ­¤ōŗ **Test Results:** {{test_results_summary}}\n    75ŌåÆ­¤ōØ **Documentation:** {{documentation_status}}\n    76ŌåÆ```\n    77ŌåÆ\n    78ŌåÆ**If FAIL:** List specific failures and required actions before story can be marked Ready for Review\n    79ŌåÆ\n    80ŌåÆ**If PASS:** Story is fully ready for code review and production consideration\n    81ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01W89Wqd4iQCSzVpohSh2yqq","session_id":"010b7052-acb2-4a98-9861-0b5f61bbdbf0","uuid":"4b106924-5935-4ab0-9f6e-719404721065","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:04:08.881Z"}
