{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AVGio5MBsaLFopXDLTNVFJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1ŌåÆ# Review Story Workflow\n     2ŌåÆname: code-review\n     3ŌåÆdescription: \"Perform an ADVERSARIAL Senior Developer code review that finds 3-10 specific problems in every story. Challenges everything: code quality, test coverage, architecture compliance, security, performance. NEVER accepts `looks good` - must find minimum issues and can auto-fix with user approval.\"\n     4ŌåÆauthor: \"BMad\"\n     5ŌåÆ\n     6ŌåÆ# Critical variables from config\n     7ŌåÆconfig_source: \"{project-root}/_bmad/bmm/config.yaml\"\n     8ŌåÆuser_name: \"{config_source}:user_name\"\n     9ŌåÆcommunication_language: \"{config_source}:communication_language\"\n    10ŌåÆuser_skill_level: \"{config_source}:user_skill_level\"\n    11ŌåÆdocument_output_language: \"{config_source}:document_output_language\"\n    12ŌåÆdate: system-generated\n    13ŌåÆplanning_artifacts: \"{config_source}:planning_artifacts\"\n    14ŌåÆimplementation_artifacts: \"{config_source}:implementation_artifacts\"\n    15ŌåÆsprint_status: \"{implementation_artifacts}/sprint-status.yaml\"\n    16ŌåÆ\n    17ŌåÆ# Workflow components\n    18ŌåÆinstalled_path: \"{project-root}/_bmad/bmm/workflows/4-implementation/code-review\"\n    19ŌåÆinstructions: \"{installed_path}/instructions.xml\"\n    20ŌåÆvalidation: \"{installed_path}/checklist.md\"\n    21ŌåÆtemplate: false\n    22ŌåÆ\n    23ŌåÆproject_context: \"**/project-context.md\"\n    24ŌåÆ\n    25ŌåÆ# Smart input file references - handles both whole docs and sharded docs\n    26ŌåÆ# Priority: Whole document first, then sharded version\n    27ŌåÆ# Strategy: SELECTIVE LOAD - only load the specific epic needed for this story review\n    28ŌåÆinput_file_patterns:\n    29ŌåÆ  architecture:\n    30ŌåÆ    description: \"System architecture for review context\"\n    31ŌåÆ    whole: \"{planning_artifacts}/*architecture*.md\"\n    32ŌåÆ    sharded: \"{planning_artifacts}/*architecture*/*.md\"\n    33ŌåÆ    load_strategy: \"FULL_LOAD\"\n    34ŌåÆ  ux_design:\n    35ŌåÆ    description: \"UX design specification (if UI review)\"\n    36ŌåÆ    whole: \"{planning_artifacts}/*ux*.md\"\n    37ŌåÆ    sharded: \"{planning_artifacts}/*ux*/*.md\"\n    38ŌåÆ    load_strategy: \"FULL_LOAD\"\n    39ŌåÆ  epics:\n    40ŌåÆ    description: \"Epic containing story being reviewed\"\n    41ŌåÆ    whole: \"{planning_artifacts}/*epic*.md\"\n    42ŌåÆ    sharded_index: \"{planning_artifacts}/*epic*/index.md\"\n    43ŌåÆ    sharded_single: \"{planning_artifacts}/*epic*/epic-{{epic_num}}.md\"\n    44ŌåÆ    load_strategy: \"SELECTIVE_LOAD\"\n    45ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013A1PTE3Sqig6Yi2KxMXRHR","session_id":"010b7052-acb2-4a98-9861-0b5f61bbdbf0","uuid":"fd0b6971-3442-4281-8e6b-ca5a50d050f6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:14:24.842Z"}
