{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0173gARBxYFaCnFWBzjioEQT","type":"tool_result","content":"     1ŌåÆ# Senior Developer Review - Validation Checklist\n     2ŌåÆ\n     3ŌåÆ- [ ] Story file loaded from `{{story_path}}`\n     4ŌåÆ- [ ] Story Status verified as reviewable (review)\n     5ŌåÆ- [ ] Epic and Story IDs resolved ({{epic_num}}.{{story_num}})\n     6ŌåÆ- [ ] Story Context located or warning recorded\n     7ŌåÆ- [ ] Epic Tech Spec located or warning recorded\n     8ŌåÆ- [ ] Architecture/standards docs loaded (as available)\n     9ŌåÆ- [ ] Tech stack detected and documented\n    10ŌåÆ- [ ] MCP doc search performed (or web fallback) and references captured\n    11ŌåÆ- [ ] Acceptance Criteria cross-checked against implementation\n    12ŌåÆ- [ ] File List reviewed and validated for completeness\n    13ŌåÆ- [ ] Tests identified and mapped to ACs; gaps noted\n    14ŌåÆ- [ ] Code quality review performed on changed files\n    15ŌåÆ- [ ] Security review performed on changed files and dependencies\n    16ŌåÆ- [ ] Outcome decided (Approve/Changes Requested/Blocked)\n    17ŌåÆ- [ ] Review notes appended under \"Senior Developer Review (AI)\"\n    18ŌåÆ- [ ] Change Log updated with review entry\n    19ŌåÆ- [ ] Status updated according to settings (if enabled)\n    20ŌåÆ- [ ] Sprint status synced (if sprint tracking enabled)\n    21ŌåÆ- [ ] Story saved successfully\n    22ŌåÆ\n    23ŌåÆ_Reviewer: {{user_name}} on {{date}}_\n    24ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013A1PTE3Sqig6Yi2KxMXRHR","session_id":"010b7052-acb2-4a98-9861-0b5f61bbdbf0","uuid":"592b6b61-d1a6-4a90-af93-96a6b1740fa6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:14:25.302Z"}
